sequenceDiagram
  participant UI as KRATOS Frontend
  participant API as FastAPI /live/snapshot
  participant Live as live_event_service
  participant Mission as mission_intelligence_service
  participant Mentor as mentor services
  participant Ctx as context services
  participant Col as collectors
  participant DB as SQLite

  UI->>API: GET /live/snapshot
  API->>Live: get_live_snapshot()
  Live->>Mission: mission lens/current mission
  Live->>Mentor: signals + next best action
  Live->>Ctx: current context + loss/drift
  Live->>Col: system/docker/git/omnis/activitywatch
  Live->>DB: checkpoints/tasks/alerts/snapshots
  DB-->>Live: persisted records
  Col-->>Live: collector status or fallback/error
  Ctx-->>Live: context payload
  Mentor-->>Live: recommendations/signals
  Mission-->>Live: mission contract
  Live-->>API: envelope with source/meta/data
  API-->>UI: JSON snapshot
  UI->>UI: render source badges and operational state

